parameters:
\SE[27]...That's all for the report. It's all my fault....
\SE[24]I will accept any punishment. \SE[36]...King Cordin.

\SE[13]No, it's fine. \SE[13]It's the first time I've
seen you make a mistake twice. \SE[14]So, the rumors were
true about that Lunaroa.
\SE[24]The king's mercy... I am extremely grateful.

\SE[5]Hehe... Stop using such formal language. We're not
that formal with each other. \SE[0]... So, what do you think
about the future?

\SE[3]First of all, without a doubt... The destination is
Ulyssean, right? \SE[44]However... It's impossible to
pursue. They are using a highly planned escape route.

\SE[3]With this, our intentions are exposed... \.ka.
\SE[0]The pacifist King of Ulyssean wouldn't be wishy-washy,
right?

\SE[14]By the way... The main force opposing us is your
student, right? It's quite ironic to be in opposition with
your own disciple. \SE[14]I imagine you must have mixed
feelings as well, don't you?

\SE[47]Good grief... You're really giving me a hard time....
\SE[24]It seems like our school's curriculum was too
excellent.

\SE[13]Because the one who wins in the end is always right.
It's only by overcoming more obstacles that we can truly
understand... \SE[14]At least, that's how I feel.
\SE[38]Bad habit... It's showing, isn't it? Your Majesty?

\SE[5]... It's fine, isn't it? After all, the things we have
to do won't change. \SE[2] No matter how we feel... Well.

\SE[14]Well... let's end the secret discussion here.
\SE[14]I want to have more secret discussions with you.

\SE[3]I've decided on your punishment. \SE[14]I want to see
you go wild on top of me. \SE[14]Please satisfy me.
